Top assister in the country last season with over 50 assists. Also scored over 30 goals from all different types of situations. One of the top talents in the current Uruguay u15 set up. Looking forward to playing later in the 2017 Copa-Sudamerica u15

Regarded by most in as one of the top up and coming central defenders in Argentina. Physically strong and brave winning most aerial battles. Very high technical level with high level of distribution to the front and midfiled. Reads the game very well which means he arrives before others to stop the danger. Was the subject of a war oif bids from both River and Boca last year making national news

Facundo has been part of both the Uruguay u15 and u17 set ups. Now is part of the u18 Uruguay set up. Very dynamic player with the ability to play in different positions. Good strength and physicality

Regarded by most in as one of the top up and coming central defenders in his age category in Uruguay. Physically strong and brave winning most aerial battles. Very high dynamic level with good speed and power. Reads the game very well which means he arrives before others to stop the danger. Played in the Copa Sudamericana with Uruguay u17 and in the same year was called up to the u18 a year young.

Has recently moved up to train with the reserva squad. Top scorer this season in a very dominant team that won the championship. Technically very strong player that creates many goals. Very clinical in front of goal converting a high ratio of chances. Also the top assister in the team as well as the top goalscorer.

Has Spanish passport in hand. Has more than a goal a game so far this season and was top scorer last season. Technical ability very high and strong on the ball physically. Very clinical in front of goal converting a high ratio of chances. Very good work ethic on and off the field of play.

Spanish passport in hand. Captain of the championship winning team in their category in Argentina. Started training with the Reserva squad at River. A physical player standing at 186cms. Technically very strong allowing his team to build from the back with him creating many offensice opportunites. Very strong in the air due not only to his physical presence but also his early reading of the game.

A leader of the defensive line for the national team. Consistent part and starter for Uruguay u15/17/18 in central defense. Vice Captain of national team. Technically very good and reads the game very early.

Top scorer in the country last season with over 25 goals. Very powerful player with good physical attributes. A genuine goal scorer from all situations. Has also started this season averaging almost a goal a game again.

National team Goalie for Urugauy U17. Physically strong and brave winning most aerial battles. Very high technical level with good distribution. Reads the game very well which means he arrives before others to stop the danger. On the verge of first team at Defensor having alredy started training there.

Started the final game for Uruguay U20 against Equador to win the Copa. Sudamericana 2017. Physically strong and brave winning 50/50 battles. A player to break the play up and then start attacks from deep. Runs from the first to last minute of every game with remarkable stamina and constant energy levels. Has strength and conditioning of the highest level.
An unbelievable physical prescence with great aerial ability. Top socrer last season for his club while playing as a second striker. Very good technical ability. Good with both left and right feet.
